<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الِاخْتِصَاصُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦٢٠. <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الِاخْتِصَاصُ»</span>: كَنِدَاءٍ دُونَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«يَا»</span> … كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَيُّهَا الْفَتَى!»</span> بِإِثْرِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ارْجُونِيَا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦٢١. وَقَدْ يُرَى ذَا دُونَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَيٍّ»</span> تِلْوَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَلْ»</span> … كَمِثْلِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«نَحْنُ - الْعُرْبَ - أَسْخَى مَنْ بَذَلْ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
